6.6 DUIM-Graphics Module

pixmap?

Generic function

Summary

Returns true if the specified object is a pixmap.

Signature

pixmap? object => pixmap?

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

pixmap?
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-graphics

Module

duim-graphics

Description

Returns true if object is a pixmap.

See also

<pixmap>, page 443
